Package edu.ucla.sspace.graph.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphReader
    A general interface for reading Graph instances for a variety of formats.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DotIO
    A class for reading graph instances from DOT graph files.
    DotWriter
    A class for reading graph instances from DOT graph files.
    EdgeListReader  
    GexfIO
    An implementation for writing Graph instances as gexf-formatted files, which are commonly used with the Gephi graph program.
    GraphMLReader
    An GraphReader implementation that supports reading files in the
    		GraphReaderAdapter  
    PajekIO
    A class for reading and writing graphs in the Pajek format.
